page.title: 05ECOLOGY
page.content: {MAJOR TREES:}Oak,Sycamore,Ash,Holly, Horse-Chestnut,Sweet-Chestnut,Scots Pine Lime-Trees, {MAJOR BIRDS:}Swallows,Sparrows,Robins Blackbirds,Starlings,Woodpigeon, Cuckoos,Herons,Ring-Doves,Woodpeckers, Great-Tits,Blue-Tits,Longtailed-Tits, Bullfinches,Greenfinches,Curlews, Chaffinches,Magpies,Goldfinches,Jays, Jackdaws,Rooks and Barn Owls. {SEA:}Gulls,Common Herons,Blackheaded Herons,Mallards,Danlings,Brent Geese, Red Wings. {MAJOR FLOWERS:}Daisy,Buttercup,Lupin, Ladies Smock,Wild Rose,Violets, Primrose,Mallow,Self Heal,Nettles,Wild Garlic. {SPECIAL FLOWERS:}Wild Lupin,Dodder,Sea Lavender,Sapphire orchid butcher broom Ladies Tresses,Early Purple Orchid. {MAJOR HEDGEROWS:}Hawthorn,Bramble,Sloe Elder,Buckthorn.
